{"tid":1455670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(推) 一定要走 唔洗放ts都捉到你","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:29:28.000Z","uid":66171,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b756b177a278e053026494f14565b2b324561169","tid":1455670,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"首先 到依家仲講緊啲咩你淨係坐無犯法唔會拉呢啲etc...都係天撚真/無智慧/鬼<br />\n<br />\n因為既然你地都知有鬼扮示威者，啲鬼一衝就搞撚掂哂你地啦，講緊直接出師有名<br />\n<br />\n係就係要逼佢回覆五大訴求，但淨坐會比起影響航空起到更大作用? 呢度point我諗你地有啲失焦，又或者係鬼啦，記住，我地係用一啲有實際目的嘅行動去逼政府正視五大訴求。<br />\n比如今日佔機場(行動)係為咗停機場本身operation(結果)去引起政府關注。 靜坐呢個<br />\n行動係唔會有實際效果。<br />\n<br />\n依家無哂機會起飛喇，今日成功咗架喇，唔走等比啲鬼伏鳩你?"},{"pid":"7a1758afd273dbf4e38fea3aa593a4234295fa48","tid":1455670,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8afd48639088cc9d1c83587547aa9d74c53b5411","tid":1455670,"uid":265839,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:15:47.000Z","msg":"無航班, 無旅客, 無必要留<br />\n只會送頭"},{"pid":"63fb5193cd16ed83185bcf749bd2b1d5090346ad","tid":1455670,"uid":304663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"走走走走"},{"pid":"115fc296cebe2d511d59d2432163bbdf6f9d1780","tid":1455670,"uid":180045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"走走走"},{"pid":"83a4a57aa1c8d0149632038f7ff661114c9e632f","tid":1455670,"uid":263534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"一定要走<br />\n咪撚信話人多就安全"},{"pid":"21dd9b0c4a197c4ff743f18cf33ec5629477b457","tid":1455670,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734a49a45e66f2b7da7934d240f79736ad7690ef","tid":1455670,"uid":280556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e9bbe0f2e3593b6ecd23f2eb2183f5e9a3337d","tid":1455670,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:16:58.000Z","msg":"今日機場留咩有咩用<br />\n你諗下你入機場的目的係咩<br />\n一 宣傳<br />\n二 不合作運動<br />\n而家冇遊客黎 一已經fail<br />\n二 成功左<br />\n唔退幾時退呀？"},{"pid":"717f47084265872c0d9304245968f0e5dfc8e35e","tid":1455670,"uid":123898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7cd6daeaad815bc01c88ebf5d7efe2046154f52","tid":1455670,"uid":264301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場唔一定要放tg先拉倒你，只要你出示唔倒有效機票，可以逐個逐個抬你地走，你未聽日入唔返機場咯，be water宜家走聽日再戰吧</span></span>"},{"pid":"1dc02a67dd9b923cedfcee7ce80b12580d40c3e1","tid":1455670,"uid":129529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"坐係到送頭 唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc89a66c403856e2a66f7dff4a1653d037549d0","tid":1455670,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7e3afe29da75585a2bb82f1d677221d61fbe9be","tid":1455670,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"無旅客即係無得宣傳啦<br />\n無得宣傳咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b238f2b736e819ee0aa595c6474507f5ee01cd0a","tid":1455670,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5ec3097ddda8fcc20ac702e67cd934254d927145","tid":1455670,"uid":11560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:20:55.000Z","msg":"一齊走"},{"pid":"3731aac67801f538833bd1170393505c3bfa44c8","tid":1455670,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UOSLkje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUOSLkje.jpg&h=831d0c00&s={SIZE}\" /